## Image pipeline environment
## Copy to .env.dev (local / Jenkins dev credential) or .env.main (Jenkins main credential).
##
## Docker (Jenkins): dev listens on 9013, main on 9003 (host + container same port).
## Local Flask: `python run.py` uses PORT below (default 8703).
##
## MEDIA_BASE_URL = public URL prefix returned in API responses (no /media suffix).
## CORS_ORIGINS   = comma-separated; include your CMS API origin(s).

# Local Flask only (ignored in Docker — gunicorn uses PORT from compose)
PORT=8703

# --- Dev (Docker host port 9013, backend on 9011) ---
# MEDIA_BASE_URL=http://YOUR_SERVER_IP:9013
# CORS_ORIGINS=http://YOUR_SERVER_IP:9011,http://YOUR_SERVER_IP:9013

# --- Main / production (reverse proxy often serves /media on CMS domain) ---
MEDIA_BASE_URL=https://cms.aspune.cloud
CORS_ORIGINS=https://cms.aspune.cloud
